OL,3,CCan Britain defend itself? Defence,
OL,4,Clocal elections and healthier school
OL,5,Cmeals
OL,7,FWatch the latest edition of Around the
OL,8,FHouse from Thursday 16 April
OL,10,FClaims from the former head of NATO
OL,11,FLord Robertson that UK is ''under-
OL,12,Fprepared'' and ''in peril'' have hit
OL,13,Fthe headlines this week, with the
OL,14,Fconflict in the Middle East also
OL,15,Fraising questions about the state of
OL,16,FBritain's military.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
